{"type": "article", "id": 2554, "title": "再生牛皮纸做的咖啡杯", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-25T07:46:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232619r1RObqjtuJG0zW5c.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师Jo Sae Bom和Jeong Lan 利用具有防水功能的再生牛皮纸材料，制作了一款名为“ CUP.FEE ”的咖啡杯，既是一款聪明环保的创意产品，又是一个独特的包装设计。将 CUP.FEE 的封口撕开，加入热水，用撕下的封口条作为搅拌棒，一杯香浓的咖啡就诞生了。虽然整个设计极尽简单，但对于想快速简便喝到速溶咖啡的人来说，是个不错的选择。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232618WxvFyeSs5KmzCjVc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232618lK8ZrYs2ygNWImuT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232619GF5Cswbn03Elk1mR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}